              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BAF2"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 4PI gamma-detector array DANCE, composed of",
                "160 BaF2 scintillators.DANCE provides the total",
                "g-ray calorimetry and the multiplicity information",
                "of the g-cascade following neutron capture. Inner",
                "radius of the array is 17 cm and the detector length",
                "i.e. thickness of the array, is 15 cm. DANCE is",
                "located on a 20 m flight path."
              ]
            }
          ],
